{
  "name": "Mark of Handling",
  "description": "You gain a 1d4 bonus to Intelligence (Nature) and Wisdom (Animal Handling) checks. You always have Animal Friendship and Speak with Animals prepared and can cast each once per long rest without a spell slot using Intelligence, Wisdom, or Charisma as your spellcasting ability. Starting at level 3, these spells can also target Monstrosities with an Intelligence of 3 or lower. Additionally, a specific list of spells is added to your spellcasting class's spell list.",
